blog.description: Welcome to my blog! ❤ If you have joined me from my fic This Love-Hate Relationship, I am honored you enjoy my fic that much. ❤ The tag for my bandfic is TLHR AU. ❤ Since I was recently asked... If you would like to create artwork for this fanfic/AUverse, please do. ❤ If you would like to create your own fanfics for this fanfic/AUverse, please do. ❤ All I ask is that you tag the AU tag in them so I can see! :D ❤ If you are joining me for other reasons, I welcome you just the same! ❤ I am happy to answer questions and chat! Shoot me an ask! Banner by the-pastel-peach. Icon art from cute avatar creator. Layout images are my edits. Hey, guys! Welcome to my blog! The name is Finn. I am a 31 year old gay trans man and I go by he/him pronouns. I have also recently come to the realization that I am a furry. Here you will mostly find reblogs of all the things I love or feel very strongly about. Besides that, I will post my fanfiction and perhaps other creations like graphics and the like. No matter what or who brought you here, I am so very glad to have you visit, even if for a short time. Finally, I never say no to asks. If you want to talk or send in some ask memes I've reblogged, feel free! I love interacting with people!

summary: i can imagine ned and peter urban exploring. and it's the middle of the day, they're in an old run down building. peters in the...
body:
i can imagine ned and peter urban exploring. and it’s the middle of the day, they’re in an old run down building. peters in the early process of honing his photography skills. and theyre walking into the basement of the structure and once theyre down the stairs, peter just.. loses it. he flails his arms, ducks, and then VIGOROUSLY pats down the top of his head.

neds just… staring at him from three steps up, and when peter looks up he just kind of points at the beam they were walking under. “there was a spiderweb”

and neds STILL staring at him, even more than before. and he just…

“dude”

“what?”

“you’re literally spider-man”

summary: I saw this drawing today of Peter Parker playing with Morgan Stark (linked here), and all I could think is that Peter is going...
body:
I saw this drawing today of Peter Parker playing with Morgan Stark (linked here), and all I could think is that Peter is going to look out for her forever. At Tony’s funeral, he promises himself he’ll look out for Tony’s family. He’s going to be there to threaten Morgan’s first boyfriend, and he will help her with her first science fair project. He’ll cheer the loudest when she wins. While doing his rounds as Spiderman, he’ll stop a robbery, and afterward, he’ll ask the owner if he can have the Iron Man bear from the window because he knows a little girl who would love it. Morgan keeps it close to her at all times. Peter is gonna be her big brother forever and that just really warms my heart <3

Peter also visits not only for Morgan but, to check in on Pepper as well. He’ll pass on composting tips that he reads on the internet or learns in his science classes. He’ll be “in the neighborhood” a lot just to check in on her and see if she needs anything. They offer each other comfort during the difficult time after Tony’s death. He only brings Pepper strawberries once, and that makes her laugh and cry all at the same time. She loves how much he loves Morgan, especially when he comes over and the two of them spend all day sitting on the floor building LEGOs and eating freeze pops. Morgan makes faces when she’s concentrating really hard which makes both Peter and Pepper laugh. This makes Pepper smile, and she realizes the gift Tony has left for Morgan, and herself, this makes the house feel a little less empty.
